title: Wolfram Research Mathematica 10.0.0 (Windows, OSX, Linux)
description:
Wolfram Research Mathematica 10.0.0
===================================

What is included

1) Mathematica_10.0.0_WIN.exe

2) Wolfram.Research.Mathematica.v9.0.0.0.Keymaker-AGAiN.7z

   - Original AGAiN keymaker for v.9.0.0 - does not work on XP,

   - Modified keymaker that works on XP,

   - All Required Dll files from "Visual C++ 2012 Redistributable".

Original AGAiN keymaker does work only on Vista, 7 and 8.
Without the Dll files included, you need to install "Visual C++ 2012 Redistributable" on every computer you run the keymaker.

3) Mathematica_10.0.0_OSX.dmg

4) Wolfram.Research.Mathematica.v9.0.0.0.MacOSX.Keymaker-AGAiN.7z

5) Mathematica_10.0.0_LINUX.sh

6) Wolfram.Research.Mathematica.v9.0.0.0.Linux.Keymaker-AGAiN.7z
